Feature: CaseExpression

  Scenario: Case should handle mixed number types
    Given any graph
    When executing query:
      """
      WITH 0.5 AS x
      WITH (CASE WHEN x < 1 THEN 1 ELSE 2.0 END) AS x
      RETURN x + 1
      """
    Then the result should be:
      | x + 1 |
      | 2     |
    And no side effects

  Scenario: Case should handle mixed types
